PSA: We are so happy with the interest potential adoptive families have in our Pomskies! While we pride ourselves on customer service, the reality is that our dogs and puppies come first. We are a family owned and run business who spends countless hours raising and caring for our beloved puppies. If a puppy or adult needs more of our attention, then we offer it, without hesitation; even if this means we are pulled from our emails and social media. This often means we are unable to answer all emails and inquiries about adoptions in as prompt a manner as we‚Äôd like. We do not have a receptionist and sometimes we are simply unable to immediately answer all interested customers.
